5ff-f3463e300000</link><description>自战争开始以来，新的限制要求进行“羞辱性”搜查，并限制律师在法庭上的活动，而囚犯则遭受暴力，有时没有代表出席听证会</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 18:01:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-prisoners-lawyers-strike-against-rights-violations-under-the-guise-of-war/0000018d-d142-d398-a5ff-f3463e300000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列政治漫画家来说，加沙战争是一场棘手的战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israels-political-cartoonists-the-gaza-war-is-a-thorny-battle/0000018d-d0f2-d398-a5ff-f2f607cd0000</link><description>漫画家游走在客观性和行动主义之间。您如何描述哈马斯的性暴力？</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 17:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israels-political-cartoonists-the-gaza-war-is-a-thorny-battle/0000018d-d0f2-d398-a5ff-f2f607cd0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列 Nova 派对常客被误认为哈马斯恐怖分子，并被以色列军队击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-partygoer-was-misidentified-as-hamas-terrorist-on-oct-7-killed-by-israeli-forces/0000018d-d14f-df79-a5cd-f17f934d0000</link><description>Ofek Atun 与女友一起逃离了户外 Nova 狂欢。他们在避难所的防空洞遭到袭击后幸存下来，然后逃到附近的阿鲁明基布兹。基布兹的志愿安全小队误认为他们是哈马斯恐怖分子，并向他们开枪</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 16:43:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nova-partygoer-was-misidentified-as-hamas-terrorist-on-oct-7-killed-by-israeli-forces/0000018d-d14f-df79-a5cd-f17f934d0000</guid></item><item><title>MAD in Lebanon：我们是否正在走向相互毁灭？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mad-in-lebanon-are-we-on-our-way-to-mutual-assured-destruction/0000018d-d06d-d3b8-af9f-dbeda6b60000</link><description>以色列有能力对黎巴嫩造成大规模破坏，但这种破坏会发生在双方身上；这种情况仍然可以避免</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 16:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true"